source does not exist.          |\n| `INTERNAL_ERROR`   | 500         | An unexpected server-side error occurred.       |\n\nReturn an error response whenever a request cannot be fulfilled, and use\nthe appropriate HTTP status code alongside the JSON body.\n```\n\n`docs/api/overview.md` already has the correct link and **requires no changes**.\n\nThe validation script (`scripts/validate_repo.py`) only checks that certain required files exist and that `mkdocs.yml` has `site_name` and `nav` — both of which remain satisfied by these changes.\n\n---\n\n**To complete this task**, the repository token needs write access (contents:write permission) so I can push the commit. Could you verify the PAT or grant push access to this repository?", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 625, "prompt_tokens": 8483, "total_tokens": 9108, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 55, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 8000, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.000782655, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.000238905, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00054375}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780984751-bAMNwrBMXsPer7nNrymw", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019eaaf6-a478-7900-b60a-b6bd0642bcd5-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 8483, "output_tokens": 625, "total_tokens": 9108, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 8000}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 55}}}}]}}}
